{"tid":1550301,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"請大家簽定一份不自殺聲明書","createTime":"2019-09-07T15:27:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T15:57:40.000Z","uid":33650,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e104f8f2dde3ce33efd2a2224507aed07c76d355","tid":1550301,"uid":33650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:27:10.000Z","msg":"如果大家無自殺既傾向,請大家寫一份中英對照既聲明<br />\n同時up上twitter同埋交低實體版本比朋友<br />\n<br />\n如果你有自殺既打算我都尊重你既決定<br />\n我想講既係 Stand With HK, Stand togather. 我希望可以全部人行落去,一個都不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%9D%8E%E6%97%BA%E9%99%BD%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6#%E5%BE%8C%E7%BA%8C%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E6%2597%25BA%25E9%2599%25BD%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6%23%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%25BA%258C%25E7%259B%25B8%25E9%2597%259C%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC18MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=8c145885\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%9D%8E%E6%97%BA%E9%99%BD%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6#%E5%BE%8C%E7%BA%8C%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6</a>"},{"pid":"6605d0044cbf40ab7c348246edd7c7df29ae3f43","tid":1550301,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:28:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f872240d4bf3549e9af9418efc9132e7256108ce","tid":1550301,"uid":33650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:28:58.000Z","msg":"仆街 串錯字, 唔準笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f7e7a353ad99f0c5bfc40cff2889128c2ae00c","tid":1550301,"uid":4273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:31:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>2019年香港自殺資料統計</ins></strong><br />\n本文件旨在記錄香港每日由新聞報導之自殺數據，以便用作討論。<br />\n本文件並非鼓吹自殺行為，請珍惜生命，關心身邊家人及朋友。<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicide\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2F2019HKsuicide&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC18MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=379bc789\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicide</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideHTML\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2F2019HKsuicideHTML&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC18MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=94b7c79f\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideHTML</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideAPI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2F2019HKsuicideAPI&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC18MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=daa45d8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideAPI</a>"},{"pid":"63fdc3f1474f3753b14ffa1f6ffd02f14d60aac8","tid":1550301,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:32:48.000Z","msg":"推 一定要交比朋友或者信任的人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最好拍多段片 放上youtube<br />\n發夢前<br />\nSet 好發佈時間<br />\n過左某日就自動上傳 <br />\n發夢前要登出<br />\n <br />\n標題大家一齊 set 做 香港示威者不自殺聲明<br />\n片中講自己名 身分證"},{"pid":"84233465a9c6e473a69fd156ee2dffc1a8cbc422","tid":1550301,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"